          <lastSummaryUpdateDate>2014-08-27T14:04:01Z</lastSummaryUpdateDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p>Repairing Our Aging Roads Act - Authorizes the Secretary of Transportation (DOT) to issue Transportation Bonds in the aggregate of up to $2 billion to each state for transportation infrastructure projects.</p> <p>Establishes in the Treasury 50 separate State Transportation Trust Funds consisting of amounts derived from the sale and issuance of Transportation Bonds to construct or improve state transportation infrastructure.</p> <p>Requires an offsetting reduction, equal to the dollar amount of bonds issued, in any discretionary account in any appropriation Act.</p>]]></text>
